---
alwaysApply: true
---

Project Name
Voice Searchable Price List System

---

PROJECT GOAL

Build a cloud-hosted system that parses complex real-world price list PDFs and allows fast search via text or voice.

System must:

* run 24/7 on free hosting
* work on phone and desktop
* support multiple PDF formats
* support fast part-number search
* handle fuzzy and voice queries

---

SUPPORTED PDF FORMATS (CRITICAL)

The system must support multiple PDF layouts.

---

FORMAT 1 – TABLE FORMAT

Structure:

designation | contents | pack_code | case_qty | price

Example:

VKTC 0904 | 2 Bearings (...) | 53 | 12 | 1425

Characteristics:

* rows may span multiple lines
* contents column may wrap
* standard table layout

---

FORMAT 2 – DUAL COLUMN FORMAT

Structure:

Product Designation | Price    Product Designation | Price

Example:

3308 A/C3 → 14,021    3317 A/C3 → 76,444

Characteristics:

* each row contains TWO products
* no pack_code or case_qty
* only designation + price
* whitespace aligned, not strict table

IMPORTANT:

Each visual row must be split into TWO separate product records.

